snippet.title: Enforcer Police Crime Action Review - Worth a Buy?
snippet.description:
Enforcer Review, is it Worth a Buy?

A new breed of Police Simulator, Enforcer demands you show exceptional bravery in the line of duty while under pressure and enemy gunfire. But is it Worth a buy?
